<h4 id="scalping-cryptocurrencies">Scalping Cryptocurrencies</h4>

<p>In 2020, crypto markets are not profiled strongly towards either ‚Äúlong term trading‚Äù or ‚Äúshort term trading‚Äù. The crypto markets have a lot of both types of traders.</p>

<p>Often, crypto traders will resort to scalping during <a href="/glossary/sideways/">sideways</a> markets situations.</p>

